org.elasticsearch.action.index

Class TransportIndexAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.common.component.AbstractComponent
      • org.elasticsearch.action.support.TransportAction<Request,Response>
        • org.elasticsearch.action.support.replication.TransportReplicationAction<Request,Request,Response>
          • org.elasticsearch.action.support.replication.TransportWriteAction<IndexRequest,IndexResponse>
            • org.elasticsearch.action.index.TransportIndexAction

  • public class TransportIndexAction
extends TransportWriteAction<IndexRequest,IndexResponse>
    Performs the index operation. Allows for the following settings:
    • autoCreateIndex: When set to true, will automatically create an index if one does not exists. Defaults to true.
    • allowIdGeneration: If the id is set not, should it be generated. Defaults to true.
